<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Communicating effectively with Turkish professors is critical to the success of the educational process. Respect and courtesy, developing sincere communication and understanding the expectations of your professors will help you in this process. Studying in Turkey is a great opportunity to not only gain academic knowledge, but also to get to know new cultures and have unforgettable experiences. You can make the most of these opportunities by improving your communication skills.</p>



