<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nostalgia strengthens the bond with the past and preserves cultural identity. It also strengthens ties between generations.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-the-advantages-of-attending-nostalgic-events">What are the advantages of attending nostalgic events?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nostalgic events offer the opportunity to keep the past alive, promote cultural richness and provide social interaction.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-is-nostalgia-seen-as-such-a-strong-emotion-in-turkey">Why is nostalgia seen as such a strong emotion in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Due to rapid social change, technological transformation and migration movements in Turkey, people believe that the past was simpler and more peaceful. This strengthens nostalgia with both personal memories and a sense of social belonging.<br></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-12-27T09:22:54Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:48:08Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/a-study-of-nostalgia-and-generational-differences-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Generational differences in Turkey shown through nostalgia with old photos and modern technology","title":"a-study-of-nostalgia-and-generational-differences-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'nostalgia-generation-differences-in-turkey' );
